727680f.title: Queens: Parsons Boulevard - Union Turnpike
727680f.text:
Parsons Boulovard, at the N.E. corner of Union Turnpike,
showing an old house, having been owned by Mrs. J. Vandeverg
in 1873 and by H. Meyer in 1891. A gasoline station was later
put up on this corner.
P. L. Sperr  March 23, 1927
